WEBVTT

00:21.230 --> 00:23.670
[Government]

00:25.370 --> 00:29.270
[Government]

00:31.320 --> 00:33.030
How did you end up like this?

00:37.320 --> 00:38.520
It was a twist of fate.

00:39.350 --> 00:40.880
Who could have foreseen it?

00:43.200 --> 00:44.390
But I have my duties.

00:45.750 --> 00:46.950
I already did my best.

00:49.350 --> 00:51.010
As the Discipline Inspector,

00:52.350 --> 00:54.560
you are responsible
for supervising the army.

00:54.560 --> 00:56.110
The rebel Sui Yuanhuai

00:56.560 --> 00:58.000
has escaped repeatedly,

00:58.640 --> 01:00.440
and you cannot escape the blame.

01:01.710 --> 01:03.310
It was indeed my negligence.

01:04.150 --> 01:07.000
I have already reported it to His Majesty

01:07.870 --> 01:09.800
and am ready to accept punishment.

01:18.789 --> 01:20.990
You have followed General He for years.

01:21.200 --> 01:22.200
You must have heard of

01:22.200 --> 01:24.510
Li Bai's poem,
"Fighting South of the Wall."

01:24.510 --> 01:26.000
"Soldiers lie wasted in the wilderness;

01:26.000 --> 01:28.260
the General's deeds amount to nothing."

01:28.310 --> 01:30.430
For the sake of so-called legitimacy,

01:30.430 --> 01:32.750
sacrificing countless innocent lives
in vain

01:32.750 --> 01:33.680
is cruel.

01:34.590 --> 01:36.150
You speak of negligence,

01:36.150 --> 01:38.680
but do you know
how many soldiers' efforts were wasted,

01:38.680 --> 01:40.610
and how many people are suffering?

01:41.640 --> 01:43.350
I am truly ashamed.

01:47.950 --> 01:50.150
As the eldest grandson of the Li family,

01:50.870 --> 01:52.039
this eternal infamy

01:53.229 --> 01:54.690
shall be borne by me alone.

01:54.979 --> 02:04.630
[Government]

01:58.560 --> 02:00.160
The futile war you provoked,

02:01.510 --> 02:03.350
and the soldiers who died unjustly...

02:03.350 --> 02:05.080
Can you bear the weight of that?

02:06.950 --> 02:07.790
Lord Li,

02:09.139 --> 02:10.800
let me remind you of one thing:

02:11.430 --> 02:14.760
do not forget why you entered the service
in the first place.

02:30.960 --> 02:32.820
What did the Marquis of Wu'an say?

02:33.000 --> 02:33.960
Xie Zheng...

02:37.750 --> 02:39.350
probably knows everything.

04:06.520 --> 04:12.010
[Pursuit of Jade]

04:12.090 --> 04:14.710
[Episode 33]

04:14.730 --> 04:21.420
[Sesame Seed Bun]

04:21.240 --> 04:23.600
What sin did the Liu family commit?

04:21.510 --> 04:29.100
[Wanted] [Notice]

04:23.750 --> 04:26.080
Their entire household was slaughtered.

04:26.750 --> 04:28.310
Bandits are ruthless.

04:28.870 --> 04:30.800
The massacre of the Liu family is nothing.

04:30.800 --> 04:32.800
All of Lin'an Town was slaughtered.

04:33.800 --> 04:36.530
No wonder the Marquis
wants to wipe out Qingfeng Stronghold.

04:36.080 --> 04:38.540
[Wanted] [Notice]

04:37.430 --> 04:39.560
He is truly ridding the people of evil.

04:39.560 --> 04:40.290
Indeed.

04:40.560 --> 04:43.159
Look at this young lady.
She looks so graceful.

04:43.400 --> 04:44.800
And yet she's a female bandit,

04:43.790 --> 04:46.250
[Sesame Seed Bun]

04:44.800 --> 04:46.510
the Chief Master of Qingfeng Stronghold?

04:46.510 --> 04:47.480
Give me five flatbreads.

04:47.480 --> 04:48.270
Okay.

04:48.360 --> 04:48.950
Pah!

04:49.340 --> 04:49.800
Here.

04:59.070 --> 05:00.530
Watch where you're going.

05:31.710 --> 05:33.159
Sui Yuanqing...

05:37.560 --> 05:38.860
You heartless thing.

05:39.870 --> 05:41.650
Where the hell are you?

05:44.630 --> 05:46.710
The government dogs are after me,

05:47.750 --> 05:49.750
and the bandits want me too.

05:50.550 --> 05:52.390
Even the 13 lives of the Liu family

05:52.390 --> 05:54.000
are pinned on me.

05:55.480 --> 05:56.659
Now I am

05:57.360 --> 05:59.680
being chased like a stray dog.

05:59.680 --> 06:00.480
But you—

06:01.430 --> 06:02.960
You are nowhere to be found.

06:29.750 --> 06:32.040
Isn't that the official from Lin'an Town?

06:32.040 --> 06:33.240
What is he doing here?

07:06.130 --> 07:09.800
[Majestic and Efficacious]

07:16.040 --> 07:18.840
Your Highness,
have some hot tea to warm yourself.

07:22.310 --> 07:24.040
We are not far from the Capital.

07:24.510 --> 07:27.510
Once we reach the Capital,
Your Highness will be safe.

07:29.750 --> 07:30.720
Qi Min!

07:31.390 --> 07:32.920
Get the hell out here!

07:40.600 --> 07:41.480
Not again.

07:42.120 --> 07:43.870
His nose is sharper than a dog's.

07:43.870 --> 07:45.800
He really wouldn't leave us alone.

08:27.600 --> 08:29.550
I'm going to kill you, you bastard,

08:29.830 --> 08:32.960
and send you to hell
to be with Father and Mother Consort.

08:33.549 --> 08:34.789
Living under someone else's name

08:34.789 --> 08:37.250
and living a stolen life
for over 10 years...

08:38.390 --> 08:40.600
I assume you have no last words.

08:42.840 --> 08:44.240
My brother, Yuanqing...

08:45.270 --> 08:47.500
You're not worthy of calling me that!

08:58.750 --> 08:59.510
Yuanqing.

09:00.480 --> 09:01.810
If you're angry with me,

09:03.000 --> 09:04.670
I apologize.

09:05.120 --> 09:06.440
Believe it or not,

09:07.480 --> 09:09.410
I never intended to hurt you at all.

09:13.080 --> 09:14.750
Never intended to hurt me?

09:15.210 --> 09:17.000
Then what about Mother Consort?

09:17.000 --> 09:18.750
How did she ever wrong you?

09:19.240 --> 09:20.000
Tell me.

09:20.480 --> 09:21.840
Tell me!

09:44.870 --> 09:46.390
Is this what you meant by

09:48.600 --> 09:50.440
never intending to hurt me?

09:52.790 --> 09:53.550
Yuanqing.

09:54.630 --> 09:56.000
I warned you long ago.

09:56.840 --> 09:58.360
Don't be too arrogant.

09:59.600 --> 10:02.260
Now I can give you
the second half of that advice.

10:03.240 --> 10:06.440
You will die a violent death.

10:23.240 --> 10:24.120
I was so stupid.

10:24.870 --> 10:27.130
I always treated you like my own brother.

10:27.600 --> 10:30.330
I couldn't even bring myself
to kill you just now.

10:34.930 --> 10:37.430
You and your family owe me this!

10:37.960 --> 10:41.090
Everyone in Lord Changxin's household
deserves to die!

10:43.580 --> 10:46.030
Why is it that
you are healthy and look energetic,

10:46.030 --> 10:48.000
while I look like a wretched ghost?

10:48.200 --> 10:49.840
Why can you practice martial arts,

10:49.840 --> 10:51.720
ride horses, and shoot arrows,

10:52.120 --> 10:56.080
while I am plagued by chronic illness
and have to drink medicine every day?

10:56.080 --> 10:57.600
The pain in my heart

10:57.910 --> 10:59.360
and the wounds on my body

11:00.030 --> 11:02.910
were caused by Lord Changxin and Wei Yan!

11:03.630 --> 11:05.430
My father and mother consort...

11:06.240 --> 11:08.150
I must avenge them.

11:08.510 --> 11:11.790
None of you will die a peaceful death!

11:16.000 --> 11:18.390
You sound so righteous.

11:20.170 --> 11:22.770
But my mother never mistreated you.

11:23.650 --> 11:26.510
On the contrary,
the Crown Princess killed her son.

11:26.600 --> 11:29.320
My mother raised you for over a decade,

11:30.000 --> 11:31.840
and you took over the mansion.

11:32.550 --> 11:35.550
How could you bring yourself to harm her?

11:38.910 --> 11:41.120
Because my heart died long ago.

11:42.440 --> 11:44.720
Of course I could do it.

11:49.840 --> 11:53.040
Your Highness, we have to go!
We cannot stay here for long.

12:25.630 --> 12:26.710
Sui Yuanqing.

12:27.840 --> 12:29.120
You forgot

12:30.000 --> 12:31.870
what I taught you.

12:32.870 --> 12:34.840
Those who are soft-hearted

12:36.550 --> 12:39.600
are not fit to stand on this battlefield,

12:40.440 --> 12:41.670
let alone dream

12:43.080 --> 12:45.270
of ruling this world.

12:54.390 --> 12:56.500
[To Know Others is Wisdom]

14:06.270 --> 14:07.130
Your Highness.

14:07.270 --> 14:08.000
I am late.

14:10.590 --> 14:12.720
You might as well show up when I'm dead.

14:14.790 --> 14:16.750
It was your Li family who sent word to me,

14:16.750 --> 14:18.480
saying everything was arranged.

14:18.480 --> 14:21.410
But what was waiting for me
throughout this journey?

14:21.630 --> 14:23.630
Xie Zheng's personal guards,

14:24.320 --> 14:26.510
and that madman, Sui Yuanqing.

14:28.320 --> 14:29.990
That was indeed my fault.

14:30.870 --> 14:32.730
Please punish me, Your Highness.

14:34.440 --> 14:36.080
I know you dislike me.

14:36.750 --> 14:38.720
Protecting and saving me

14:39.000 --> 14:41.600
is merely obeying
your grandfather's orders.

14:42.080 --> 14:44.080
Since you have decided to join us,

14:44.240 --> 14:46.300
there is absolutely no turning back.

14:47.240 --> 14:49.570
Only by escorting me safely to the Capital

14:50.080 --> 14:52.610
will your Li family
stand a chance of winning,

14:52.670 --> 14:55.070
and your years of planning
won't be in vain.

14:57.200 --> 14:58.120
Otherwise,

14:58.600 --> 15:00.330
I will drag you all down with me.

15:00.840 --> 15:03.370
Not only will the entire Li clan
be destroyed,

15:03.790 --> 15:06.520
but Wei Yan will also remain in power
for decades,

15:06.870 --> 15:08.800
with the common people suffering.

15:13.960 --> 15:16.120
I heard you care for the people.

15:17.360 --> 15:20.820
You wouldn't want to see
the chaos of war rise again, would you?

15:23.030 --> 15:23.720
I...

15:25.360 --> 15:26.480
will do my best.

15:28.630 --> 15:29.320
Also,

15:30.440 --> 15:32.240
I don't care what method you use,

15:33.080 --> 15:34.670
kill Yu Bao'er for me.

15:35.200 --> 15:37.440
Bring Yu Qianqian back unharmed.

15:37.860 --> 15:41.620
[Majestic and Efficacious]

15:38.750 --> 15:39.610
Your Highness.

15:40.960 --> 15:43.490
I heard Yu Bao'er
is your only flesh and blood.

15:44.200 --> 15:45.600
I do not acknowledge him.

15:45.670 --> 15:47.800
This bloodline will be the death of me.

15:49.080 --> 15:50.120
A worthless life

15:50.750 --> 15:52.390
compared to the entire Li clan—

15:52.390 --> 15:55.320
you should know which weighs heavier.

16:15.570 --> 16:20.120
[Merciful White Dragon Temple]

16:17.120 --> 16:19.120
If you cannot find the person I seek,

16:19.510 --> 16:21.270
my alliance with your Li clan

16:21.790 --> 16:22.910
ends here.

16:32.430 --> 16:33.960
Disregarding
the kindness of his upbringing,

16:33.960 --> 16:35.360
killing his brother,

16:35.480 --> 16:37.210
and hunting down his own child.

16:38.240 --> 16:40.570
How can a heartless and unjust man
like him

16:40.960 --> 16:42.240
be Emperor?

16:44.790 --> 16:46.190
If he ascends the throne,

16:46.960 --> 16:48.820
he will surely not be a wise ruler.

16:51.550 --> 16:52.360
Grandfather,

16:53.770 --> 16:55.140
you are truly wrong.

17:42.750 --> 17:43.960
You're not dead yet?

17:50.030 --> 17:51.000
Kill me

17:52.690 --> 17:54.290
to avenge yourself.

17:58.070 --> 17:59.400
All right.

18:03.950 --> 18:05.110
Sui Yuanqing.

18:07.580 --> 18:08.780
Then before you die,

18:12.270 --> 18:14.200
there's something I'd like to ask.

18:17.920 --> 18:20.260
Have you ever really liked me?

18:29.640 --> 18:31.700
I, Sui Yuanqing, throughout my life,

18:32.350 --> 18:34.210
have deceived countless people.

18:36.440 --> 18:37.920
Now that I'm about to die,

18:40.070 --> 18:41.270
logically speaking,

18:42.240 --> 18:43.750
I should spin some lies

18:45.700 --> 18:47.500
to make you risk your life for me.

18:49.590 --> 18:51.510
But it's really strange.

18:54.920 --> 18:57.440
I don't want to lie
to you at all right now.

19:01.820 --> 19:02.970
I've never

19:05.270 --> 19:07.610
truly liked you.

19:17.270 --> 19:18.900
Look at yourself.

19:20.880 --> 19:22.360
It's best you never did.

19:30.510 --> 19:31.900
Without you,

19:34.830 --> 19:36.480
my life ahead

19:39.310 --> 19:41.200
will be incredibly carefree.

19:56.160 --> 19:58.110
If you can survive,

19:59.000 --> 20:00.000
take this

20:01.400 --> 20:03.110
and find Fan Changyu.

20:08.250 --> 20:09.270
What is this?

20:13.310 --> 20:15.310
You were together before after all.

20:16.350 --> 20:17.880
I'm leaving you a way out.

20:19.550 --> 20:22.830
Qi Min wants the whole world to suffer.

20:23.590 --> 20:24.920
I, Sui Yuanqing,

20:26.240 --> 20:28.640
only want him to suffer alone.

20:30.240 --> 20:31.920
Why would she believe me?

20:56.550 --> 20:58.440
Then I will give you a

21:02.400 --> 21:04.110
pledge of loyalty.

21:34.510 --> 21:36.210
Sui Yuanqing!

21:45.900 --> 21:48.520
[Three days later]

21:47.920 --> 21:48.720
Your Majesty,

21:48.920 --> 21:50.750
I have a matter to report.

21:51.070 --> 21:52.680
Wei Yan lacks discipline
over his subordinates.

21:52.680 --> 21:54.270
This act is tantamount to rebellion.

21:54.270 --> 21:56.070
It must be punished severely.

22:01.920 --> 22:04.550
Grand Tutor, you understand me.
Speak freely.

22:05.030 --> 22:05.830
Your Majesty.

22:06.110 --> 22:07.070
The Marquis of Wu'an

22:07.070 --> 22:09.480
is the nephew personally cultivated
by Prime Minister Wei.

22:09.480 --> 22:10.750
Yet, in front of the troops,

22:10.750 --> 22:14.350
he sliced off the ear of Eunuch Li,
who was delivering the decree.

22:14.350 --> 22:16.960
Such behavior is incredibly arrogant.

22:16.960 --> 22:18.400
It is truly treasonous.

22:18.400 --> 22:21.260
By law, he should be executed
as a warning to others.

22:24.200 --> 22:26.270
Grand Tutor Li speaks frankly.

22:28.200 --> 22:30.330
Prime Minister Wei, what is your view?

22:30.830 --> 22:32.200
In my opinion...

22:33.200 --> 22:34.350
This Eunuch Li

22:34.590 --> 22:38.560
kept claiming
the Marquis of Wu'an intended to rebel.

22:38.680 --> 22:40.200
However, I believe

22:40.680 --> 22:44.000
the Marquis
merely lost control in his anger.

22:45.270 --> 22:46.350
After all, in this world,

22:46.350 --> 22:49.310
not everyone can be a modest gentleman

22:49.310 --> 22:52.440
like Grand Tutor Li's grandson,
Discipline Inspector Li.

22:52.440 --> 22:54.850
Even if Your Majesty
suddenly changed your mind

22:54.850 --> 22:57.400
about marrying the Princess Royal
to someone else,

22:57.400 --> 23:00.200
he could accept it gladly.

23:05.640 --> 23:07.970
What Prime Minister Wei said is also true.

23:09.000 --> 23:10.550
Military commanders

23:10.790 --> 23:13.270
are rough men.

23:19.200 --> 23:20.330
Prime Minister Wei!

23:20.880 --> 23:23.030
He Jingyuan's control over half the army

23:23.030 --> 23:25.480
has fallen into the hands
of a mere village girl.

23:25.480 --> 23:29.440
That Commandant Fan cannot even
read military maps or treatises,

23:29.440 --> 23:31.440
yet because of your selfish motives,

23:31.440 --> 23:33.720
she became an Army Supervisor
in Jizhou Prefecture.

23:33.720 --> 23:35.680
The Command Office is in chaos.

23:35.880 --> 23:38.340
May I ask,
where is the military discipline?

23:38.350 --> 23:40.080
And where is the law of the land?

23:40.110 --> 23:41.540
Is that so?

23:44.940 --> 23:45.740
Your Majesty!

23:45.880 --> 23:47.750
The Marquis of Wu'an and Commandant Fan

23:47.750 --> 23:49.550
have both made
distinguished military contributions.

23:49.550 --> 23:50.960
But rewards and punishments
should be clearly distinct—

23:50.960 --> 23:52.550
they cannot be conflated.

23:52.550 --> 23:54.720
What do you think, Your Majesty?

23:57.480 --> 23:58.960
Report!

24:00.310 --> 24:01.110
Your Majesty.

24:01.310 --> 24:03.770
This is an 800-li urgent report
from Jizhou.

24:03.790 --> 24:04.440
Present it at once.

24:04.440 --> 24:05.070
Yes.

24:14.000 --> 24:15.110
Excellent!

24:15.920 --> 24:18.480
The Marquis of Wu'an and Commandant Fan
have joined forces.

24:18.480 --> 24:20.810
The rebel Sui Yuanhuai has been executed.

24:20.830 --> 24:23.350
Lord Changxin and his two sons
are all dead.

24:23.830 --> 24:25.070
The Sui family line is severed.

24:25.070 --> 24:27.720
From now on, there are no more
Chongzhou rebels in this world.

24:27.720 --> 24:28.250
Perfect!

24:33.920 --> 24:38.320
A perfect harmony between General
and Minister defeating the enemy together.

24:38.640 --> 24:40.940
This is my great fortune.

24:41.070 --> 24:43.240
And a blessing for the Great Yin.

24:46.790 --> 24:51.200
Worldly affairs are like chess;
every game is new.

24:51.830 --> 24:55.550
Since the Marquis of Wu'an and Commandant Fan
have achieved consecutive victories,

24:55.550 --> 24:57.350
I shall reward them.

24:57.510 --> 24:59.310
I shall reward them generously.

24:59.440 --> 25:01.000
Your Majesty is wise.

25:03.900 --> 25:05.200
Your Majesty is wise.

25:07.190 --> 25:10.240
[Government]

25:10.340 --> 25:18.340
[Peace at the border]

25:22.440 --> 25:22.960
My Lord.

25:23.490 --> 25:25.830
The Princess Royal
is about to return to the capital.

25:25.830 --> 25:28.790
Commandant Fan is holding
a farewell banquet for her tonight.

25:28.790 --> 25:29.790
Will you be going?

25:47.120 --> 25:47.810
Also,

25:48.140 --> 25:48.880
tomorrow morning,

25:48.880 --> 25:52.610
the Marquis is sending massed troops
to escort the Princess Royal.

26:06.640 --> 26:08.240
I am too ashamed to face them.

26:21.550 --> 26:22.880
Come on, come on.

26:22.880 --> 26:24.480
Come on.

26:35.440 --> 26:36.140
Here.

26:36.170 --> 26:37.020
Here.

26:38.040 --> 26:40.210
[Qinwen Hall]

26:44.160 --> 26:44.720
Come on.

26:44.740 --> 26:45.680
-Ten.
-Twenty.

26:53.270 --> 26:55.590
It's getting messy with all the drinking.

26:55.590 --> 26:58.120
Why hasn't
Discipline Inspector Li come yet?

26:58.790 --> 27:00.240
He caught a cold.

27:00.510 --> 27:02.040
He probably cannot make it.

27:04.550 --> 27:05.240
Everyone.

27:06.450 --> 27:07.790
I cannot hold my liquor well.

27:07.790 --> 27:09.720
I will take my leave after this cup.

27:24.750 --> 27:26.210
Farewell, Your Highness.

27:36.830 --> 27:37.530
Sit.

27:42.960 --> 27:45.270
The Princess Royal
returns to the palace tomorrow.

27:45.270 --> 27:47.920
If anyone has anything to say,

27:47.960 --> 27:49.560
do not let tonight slip away.

27:51.510 --> 27:52.030
I'll go.

27:51.960 --> 27:54.000
[Qinwen Hall]

27:52.030 --> 27:52.760
You sit down!

27:52.880 --> 27:53.510
All right.

27:57.400 --> 27:58.640
Go on!

28:00.790 --> 28:02.120
What does he have to say?

28:03.350 --> 28:04.340
Will he go?

28:04.400 --> 28:05.240
H-He's going.

28:06.350 --> 28:07.210
Your Highness!

28:07.510 --> 28:09.110
Your Highness, please wait!

28:10.160 --> 28:10.640
Your Highness.

28:10.640 --> 28:11.790
The Princess Royal
doesn't want to see you.

28:11.790 --> 28:12.750
I just want to ask a few questions.

28:12.750 --> 28:13.440
Go away!

28:15.270 --> 28:16.160
I imagine Your Highness wouldn't want

28:16.160 --> 28:19.690
to return to the palace
with regrets and unanswered questions.

28:25.190 --> 28:26.250
Leave us, Jianjia.

28:34.270 --> 28:35.020
Allow me.

28:41.680 --> 28:42.540
Your Highness.

28:43.960 --> 28:45.200
I actually want to ask,

28:45.200 --> 28:47.730
why are you
suddenly returning to the palace?

28:48.590 --> 28:51.120
I have been
in the Northwest for over 5 months.

28:51.790 --> 28:53.160
I feel exhausted.

28:54.640 --> 28:56.900
I've also suddenly realized something—

28:57.350 --> 29:00.880
I don't want to waste any more time
on pointless entanglements.

29:01.550 --> 29:04.010
I assume you must be greatly relieved.

29:07.200 --> 29:09.400
Since Your Highness has realized this,

29:09.590 --> 29:12.190
I should naturally offer
my congratulations.

29:12.400 --> 29:14.060
However, there are some words

29:14.960 --> 29:16.590
that I have kept hidden
in my heart for a long time

29:16.590 --> 29:18.790
that I wish to share
with Your Highness.

29:19.160 --> 29:20.680
But my clan's rules are strict,

29:20.680 --> 29:22.610
and I dared not overstep my bounds.

29:24.400 --> 29:25.590
So, a few days ago,

29:27.030 --> 29:28.230
I returned to Hejian.

29:29.880 --> 29:32.740
I knelt in the ancestral hall
for 3 days and 3 nights,

29:33.680 --> 29:36.680
and finally obtained
the clan leader's forgiveness.

29:36.790 --> 29:37.930
Only then do I dare

29:39.200 --> 29:41.060
to reveal my feelings to you here.

29:44.200 --> 29:45.160
Go on.

29:48.050 --> 29:48.850
Fan!

29:51.270 --> 29:52.110
-I…
-Slowly.

29:52.510 --> 29:55.070
I have to have a few drinks
with you alone.

29:55.400 --> 29:57.130
Do you still... have wine here?

29:58.800 --> 30:00.800
I... Let me speak from the heart.

30:02.200 --> 30:04.650
I, Jin, have never admired anyone.

30:04.790 --> 30:06.040
But I admire you.

30:06.830 --> 30:08.310
Before I met you,

30:08.750 --> 30:10.640
I never believed

30:10.640 --> 30:13.720
that a woman
with such thin arms and legs like you

30:13.720 --> 30:15.490
could go on battlefields.

30:16.230 --> 30:18.480
Can this small body
of yours go on battlefields?

30:18.480 --> 30:19.350
Never heard of it.

30:19.350 --> 30:20.310
Fan can.

30:20.400 --> 30:22.590
So I admire you.

30:22.590 --> 30:24.880
My boys all admire you.

30:24.880 --> 30:25.340
Come on.

30:30.200 --> 30:30.900
Come!

30:32.110 --> 30:33.590
-Cheers to Fan.
-Come on.

30:33.590 --> 30:34.480
-Come on.
-Come on.

30:34.480 --> 30:35.270
Brothers!

30:35.310 --> 30:35.830
Pour the wine.

30:35.830 --> 30:36.640
Pour, pour.

30:37.350 --> 30:38.720
My wife can't hold her liquor well.

30:38.720 --> 30:39.480
I'll drink for her.

30:39.480 --> 30:40.180
Here.

30:41.680 --> 30:43.340
What wife?

30:44.110 --> 30:46.200
She is the head of your family.

30:47.000 --> 30:48.590
Everyone in Lin'an knows

30:48.770 --> 30:50.890
you are the matrilocal husband
of the Fan family.

30:50.890 --> 30:53.510
Once you married in, you have to listen
to the head of the house.

30:53.510 --> 30:54.200
Isn't that right?

30:54.200 --> 30:54.790
Exactly.

30:54.790 --> 30:57.310
You usually dress like a gentleman.

30:57.310 --> 31:00.070
Yes, you're the Marquis of Wu'an.

31:00.350 --> 31:01.790
But you can't deny

31:01.790 --> 31:03.590
the marriage vows you took.

31:03.590 --> 31:04.990
You can't just deny them.

31:06.880 --> 31:09.350
Forget about
this matrilocal husband nonsense.

31:09.350 --> 31:10.550
I can drink this wine.

31:24.000 --> 31:26.400
-I'm old. I don't remember what I said.
-Sit, sit.

31:26.400 --> 31:27.550
I have a low tolerance for alcohol,

31:27.550 --> 31:29.350
so I didn't hold the cup steadily.

31:29.350 --> 31:31.350
My wife and I will take our leave now.

31:31.680 --> 31:32.830
Take your time drinking, everyone!

31:32.830 --> 31:33.590
Fan!

31:34.030 --> 31:34.720
Hey!

31:36.720 --> 31:37.720
A hundred years ago,

31:37.720 --> 31:41.670
[Dingcang Pavilion]

31:38.590 --> 31:41.240
the Gongsun clan was once in its prime.

31:42.750 --> 31:45.480
All past Empresses
came from the Gongsun family.

31:47.240 --> 31:49.040
But a tall tree catches the wind.

31:49.390 --> 31:50.990
And they all met a tragic end.

31:51.720 --> 31:53.650
When the Great Ancestor was alive,

31:54.160 --> 31:56.690
a dragon robe
was found in the Eastern Palace.

31:58.300 --> 32:01.030
Crown Prince Shaoyang
was demoted to a commoner.

32:02.510 --> 32:04.840
The two Empresses from the Gongsun family

32:05.070 --> 32:06.920
hanged themselves in the palace.

32:06.920 --> 32:07.990
The Gongsun clan

32:08.830 --> 32:11.030
had their homes raided and were exiled.

32:12.790 --> 32:15.530
Even the plaque
at Luyuan Academy's Library

32:16.000 --> 32:17.260
was nearly taken back.

32:18.960 --> 32:20.420
I know about this.

32:21.270 --> 32:22.440
The Gongsun case

32:23.270 --> 32:24.570
was eventually proven

32:25.790 --> 32:28.000
to be a frame-up by a prince.

32:31.240 --> 32:32.430
In this world,

32:32.720 --> 32:35.250
there is no such thing
as a flawless frame-up.

32:35.400 --> 32:38.160
It was just that the Emperor
on the throne back then

32:38.160 --> 32:40.690
could no longer tolerate
the Gongsun family.

32:41.550 --> 32:43.010
The Gongsun branch family

32:43.360 --> 32:46.560
has struggled to survive at Luyuan Academy
for a century.

32:48.110 --> 32:50.400
The first rule set for the clan was:

32:51.350 --> 32:52.810
do not enter officialdom.

32:57.200 --> 32:58.070
Actually,

32:59.670 --> 33:03.000
from the first day Your Highness arrived
at Luyuan Academy,

33:03.000 --> 33:04.480
I knew you were a woman.

33:06.170 --> 33:07.110
When you played

33:07.110 --> 33:09.710
that first game of chess
with me at the Library,

33:09.920 --> 33:11.030
I already knew

33:12.590 --> 33:13.680
that the person
who broke my chess formation

33:13.680 --> 33:15.400
at Fengyu Pavilion was you.

33:17.880 --> 33:18.550
However,

33:21.070 --> 33:23.400
when I found out
the girl I had long admired

33:24.760 --> 33:27.090
was actually
the current Princess Royal,

33:27.880 --> 33:29.430
I felt no joy in my heart.

33:32.070 --> 33:34.130
I only lamented how fate toys with me.

33:35.510 --> 33:37.720
Then why are you telling me

33:39.720 --> 33:40.830
this now?

33:51.680 --> 33:53.610
I want to propose to Your Highness.

33:56.510 --> 33:57.200
I...

33:59.550 --> 34:01.350
have admired you for a long time.

34:01.480 --> 34:04.070
Today, I boldly ask Your Highness:

34:05.260 --> 34:06.200
if one day,

34:07.310 --> 34:08.480
after I help Jiuheng

34:09.110 --> 34:11.110
bring down Wei Yan and the Li family,

34:13.000 --> 34:14.530
would you, Princess Royal,

34:15.150 --> 34:17.070
be willing to live with me in Hejian

34:17.070 --> 34:18.590
as a carefree couple?

34:25.630 --> 34:26.960
You can rest assured.

34:27.840 --> 34:29.230
The Gongsun family
has accumulated wealth for a century

34:29.230 --> 34:30.190
and still has some assets,

34:30.190 --> 34:31.449
I won't let you suffer.

34:32.000 --> 34:35.090
-It's just that Hejian's no match to—
-What if I say no?

34:49.070 --> 34:49.929
In that case...

34:54.510 --> 34:55.880
I spoke out of turn.

34:57.280 --> 34:59.080
Please forgive my foolishness.

35:13.140 --> 35:14.390
Gongsun Blockhead.

35:17.350 --> 35:18.180
I

35:19.280 --> 35:21.890
want the thousands of books
in your library

35:22.480 --> 35:23.740
as the betrothal gift.

35:24.590 --> 35:25.590
Do you agree?

35:31.880 --> 35:33.010
You're hesitating?

35:37.960 --> 35:39.020
Y-Yes.

35:39.110 --> 35:40.640
Yes. I agree to everything.

35:41.810 --> 35:44.400
My family has 12 library buildings.

35:45.280 --> 35:46.410
I wonder, Princess,

35:47.110 --> 35:48.440
which one do you want?

35:48.800 --> 35:49.800
I want them all!

35:52.450 --> 35:53.000
Okay.

35:55.510 --> 35:56.110
Okay.

36:02.110 --> 36:04.070
Don't pull me.

36:08.500 --> 36:10.460
Where are you taking me?

36:11.670 --> 36:13.590
You're drunk.
I'm taking you back to your room.

36:13.590 --> 36:14.120
Let's go.

36:14.280 --> 36:16.320
I'm not drunk, Your Lordship.

36:22.760 --> 36:24.070
You can't change

36:25.560 --> 36:27.090
how you address me, can you?

36:30.630 --> 36:32.230
Except for "Your Lordship,"

36:32.750 --> 36:34.610
you can call me whatever you want.

36:37.360 --> 36:40.840
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

36:41.410 --> 36:44.010
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

36:44.640 --> 36:48.020
♪ For a chance encounter ♪

36:49.200 --> 36:52.830
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

36:53.170 --> 36:55.410
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

36:54.760 --> 36:56.230
Yan Zheng...

36:55.770 --> 36:59.280
♪ Just for a glance ♪

36:57.440 --> 36:58.700
Your name is Yan Zheng.

36:59.580 --> 37:00.340
♪ In this life ♪

37:00.360 --> 37:02.950
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

37:02.970 --> 37:04.630
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

37:05.010 --> 37:05.860
♪ On this journey ♪

37:05.070 --> 37:06.070
Can I call you

37:05.890 --> 37:08.680
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

37:07.070 --> 37:09.280
Yan Zheng in the future?

37:08.700 --> 37:10.750
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

37:10.780 --> 37:11.630
♪ After we part ♪

37:11.650 --> 37:14.640
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

37:14.670 --> 37:16.980
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

37:17.000 --> 37:21.630
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

37:21.960 --> 37:25.360
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

37:22.430 --> 37:24.030
Your hand...

37:26.000 --> 37:26.880
Does it hurt?

37:28.800 --> 37:32.270
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

37:32.630 --> 37:35.470
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

37:36.080 --> 37:39.300
♪ For a chance encounter ♪

37:40.530 --> 37:44.120
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

37:44.610 --> 37:46.950
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

37:47.150 --> 37:47.960
Changyu...

37:47.210 --> 37:50.670
♪ Just for a glance ♪

37:51.020 --> 37:51.780
♪ In this life ♪

37:51.510 --> 37:52.360
Kiss me.

37:51.800 --> 37:54.390
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

37:54.410 --> 37:56.160
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

37:56.450 --> 37:57.500
♪ On this journey ♪

37:57.520 --> 38:00.370
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

38:00.400 --> 38:02.190
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

38:02.220 --> 38:03.040
♪ After we part ♪

38:03.060 --> 38:05.980
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

38:06.000 --> 38:08.300
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

38:08.320 --> 38:13.000
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

38:13.880 --> 38:14.700
♪ In this life ♪

38:14.720 --> 38:17.480
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

38:17.500 --> 38:19.070
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

38:19.560 --> 38:20.480
♪ On this journey ♪

38:20.500 --> 38:23.270
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

38:23.290 --> 38:25.210
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

38:25.240 --> 38:26.180
♪ After we part ♪

38:26.210 --> 38:28.950
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

38:29.020 --> 38:31.350
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

38:31.420 --> 38:35.510
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

38:36.470 --> 38:40.750
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

38:53.510 --> 38:54.320
If you miss me,

38:54.320 --> 38:55.720
you can write me a letter.

38:56.110 --> 38:57.770
Even though I can't read them.

39:02.480 --> 39:03.540
I'll be going now.

39:04.220 --> 39:05.050
Safe travels.

39:27.760 --> 39:28.490
I'm leaving.

39:55.030 --> 39:56.710
Since you can't bear to part with her,

39:56.710 --> 39:58.310
why not see her off yourself?

39:58.630 --> 39:59.880
If I went,

39:59.880 --> 40:01.680
I'm afraid I wouldn't let her go.

40:06.400 --> 40:07.590
A move played cannot be taken back.

40:07.590 --> 40:09.450
What I promised you still stands.

40:10.230 --> 40:11.880
How am I the one holding you back

40:11.880 --> 40:13.210
and ruining your plans?

40:15.030 --> 40:16.810
We have already promised each other.

40:16.810 --> 40:17.930
Once this is over,

40:17.960 --> 40:19.630
we will return to Hejian together,

40:19.630 --> 40:22.320
find a quiet place,
and spend the rest of our lives in peace.

40:22.320 --> 40:24.150
The Capital is treacherous.

40:24.150 --> 40:26.080
It is indeed imperative to act now.

40:27.320 --> 40:29.180
It is time to return to the Capital

40:29.710 --> 40:31.320
and finish what needs to be done,

40:31.320 --> 40:32.400
once and for all.

40:36.520 --> 40:42.250
[Capital]

40:48.900 --> 40:50.110
Not bad, not bad.

40:53.550 --> 40:54.780
Drink some more.

40:55.190 --> 40:56.070
I want to eat this.

40:56.070 --> 40:56.590
Here.

40:56.670 --> 40:57.230
Okay.

40:59.960 --> 41:00.920
Stop it.

41:00.920 --> 41:02.320
Have another drink.

41:04.510 --> 41:05.480
Mr. Li?

41:07.800 --> 41:11.330
I was wondering why I haven't seen
Ms. Yueli these past few days.

41:13.240 --> 41:17.100
Turns out someone is hogging
the Jingque Tower and refusing to leave.

41:23.110 --> 41:24.320
Wei!

41:24.880 --> 41:27.740
Aren't you supposed
to be serving in the Northwest?

41:28.360 --> 41:36.150
[Grand Tutor Li's grandson,
Li Huaixian]

41:30.480 --> 41:32.810
I heard the Marquis of Wu'an has returned.

41:34.070 --> 41:36.600
Did you step down
to make way for your betters?

41:45.230 --> 41:45.840
Get lost.

41:49.880 --> 41:51.400
As expected, bastards

41:51.400 --> 41:53.660
are never as good as the biological ones.

41:55.670 --> 41:57.530
It seems that the Marquis of Wu'an

41:57.710 --> 42:00.170
is Prime Minister Wei's
own flesh and blood.

42:01.000 --> 42:02.060
Everyone, get out.

42:03.480 --> 42:04.190
Yes, Sir.

42:19.000 --> 42:20.920
Say that again.

42:22.000 --> 42:23.130
Why play dumb?

42:23.400 --> 42:25.460
Word has spread all over the Capital.

42:25.550 --> 42:28.150
The Prime Minister
and his wife are estranged.

42:28.780 --> 42:31.180
You are not Prime Minister Wei's son
at all.

42:36.880 --> 42:37.480
Wei Xuan!

42:37.480 --> 42:38.210
How dare you!

42:40.650 --> 42:42.090
You're just a bastard.

42:42.660 --> 42:45.670
Lying to people all day
using Prime Minister Wei's name.

42:45.670 --> 42:47.000
Your mother is nothing!

42:47.320 --> 42:48.670
I've long heard
that the Prime Minister's true love

42:48.670 --> 42:51.670
is his childhood sweetheart
from the palace, Lady Qi.

42:53.320 --> 42:54.540
Li...

42:55.070 --> 42:56.620
You're full of crap!

42:56.840 --> 42:57.840
If we were on the battlefield,

42:57.840 --> 42:59.640
I would have killed you already.

43:00.590 --> 43:02.190
I'll give you one chance.

43:02.360 --> 43:05.160
Shout three times
that "The Li is inferior to Wei,"

43:05.590 --> 43:07.590
and I'll let you off today.

43:07.650 --> 43:08.360
Pah!

43:08.670 --> 43:10.530
Who do you think you are, Wei Xuan?

43:10.550 --> 43:11.950
The Li is inferior to Wei?

43:12.000 --> 43:14.000
More like the Wei is inferior to Xie!

43:16.920 --> 43:17.710
Wei Xuan!

43:23.140 --> 43:25.640
[Post-Credits Scene]

44:02.200 --> 44:09.210
[Qinwen Hall]

44:04.280 --> 44:05.740
F-Fan and His Lordship...

44:05.920 --> 44:07.110
Th-Th-They...

44:07.110 --> 44:07.910
What's wrong?

44:08.480 --> 44:09.590
Come look for yourself.

44:09.590 --> 44:10.550
Look, look!

44:13.440 --> 44:14.240
His Lordship—

44:14.320 --> 44:15.400
What Lordship?

44:15.400 --> 44:17.000
I'm still mad at him.

44:17.400 --> 44:20.280
One minute he's lowering his status
to be Fan's matrilocal husband,

44:20.280 --> 44:22.630
then he's throwing
his weight around as a marquis.

44:22.630 --> 44:25.230
Now he's going to marry the princess
and become a Prince Consort.

44:25.230 --> 44:26.190
I'm telling you,

44:26.510 --> 44:27.590
if he really dares

44:27.590 --> 44:28.710
to wrong Fan,

44:29.670 --> 44:30.400
I'll...

44:30.700 --> 44:31.340
I'll...

44:31.750 --> 44:32.380
I'll...

44:33.070 --> 44:34.400
What are you gonna do?

44:34.310 --> 44:37.360
[Qinwen Hall]

44:35.190 --> 44:36.760
I'll stay mad at him!
